TITLE: CommandBus with AutowireIterator for Tagged Services
DESCRIPTION: Implementation showing how to use AutowireIterator to collect and iterate over tagged command handlers.
SOURCE: https://github.com/symfony/symfony-docs/blob/7.3/service_container/service_subscribers_locators.rst#2025-04-22_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
namespace App;

use App\CommandHandler\BarHandler;
use App\CommandHandler\FooHandler;
use Psr\Container\ContainerInterface;
use Symfony\Component\DependencyInjection\Attribute\AutowireIterator;

class CommandBus
{
    public function __construct(
        #[AutowireIterator('command_handler')]
        private iterable $handlers,
    ) {
    }

    public function handle(Command $command): mixed
    {
        foreach ($this->handlers as $handler) {
            if ($handler->supports($command)) {
                return $handler->handle($command);
            }
        }
    }
}
```

