TITLE: Configuring the Serializer with ClassDiscriminator for Interfaces in Symfony
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to manually configure the Symfony Serializer with ClassDiscriminatorFromClassMetadata to handle interfaces and abstract classes when using the standalone implementation.
