TITLE: Standalone String Hashing Example
DESCRIPTION: Example of using PasswordHasherFactory to hash and verify strings independently of users.
SOURCE: https://github.com/symfony/symfony-docs/blob/7.3/security/passwords.rst#2025-04-22_snippet_26

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use Symfony\Component\PasswordHasher\Hasher\PasswordHasherFactory;

// configure different hashers via the factory
$factory = new PasswordHasherFactory([
    'common' => ['algorithm' => 'bcrypt'],
    'sodium' => ['algorithm' => 'sodium'],
]);

// retrieve the hasher using bcrypt
$hasher = $factory->getPasswordHasher('common');
$hash = $hasher->hash('plain');

// verify that a given string matches the hash calculated above
$hasher->verify($hash, 'invalid'); // false
$hasher->verify($hash, 'plain'); // true
```

