TITLE: Extracting Metadata from Annotations using PhpStanExtractor (Symfony PHP)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates using Symfony\Component\PropertyInfo\Extractor\PhpStanExtractor to extract type and description information from PHP annotations such as @var, @param, and @return. It includes a class example with a constructor parameter and usage of the PhpStanExtractor for type and documentation retrieval. Dependencies include the phpstan/phpdoc-parser and phpdocumentor/reflection-docblock packages, and the extractor is available starting with Symfony 7.3.
