DESCRIPTION: Shows how to deserialize incoming JSON request data into a `Person` object within a Symfony controller. It retrieves the raw request content, checks the content type, and uses the injected `SerializerInterface`'s `deserialize` method, specifying the target class (`Person::class`) and the input format ('json').
