TITLE: Chaining Multiple Symfony Context Builders for Complex Contexts in PHP
DESCRIPTION: This PHP example demonstrates how to chain multiple context builders (ObjectNormalizerContextBuilder and CsvEncoderContextBuilder) to create a complex serialization context. It starts with a custom array, adds group-based settings, and specifies a delimiter for CSV output. This is useful for advanced serialization scenarios requiring layered configuration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/symfony/symfony-docs/blob/7.3/serializer.rst#2025-04-22_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: php
