TITLE: Deprecating a Service Alias via Configuration Files
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to mark a service alias (`app.mailer`) as deprecated in YAML, XML, and PHP configuration files. This triggers a deprecation warning when the alias is used. A package name, version, and an optional custom message (using the `%alias_id%` placeholder) can be specified.
