TITLE: Casting Health Check Method Environment Variable using Constant Processor in Symfony with PHP Configuration
DESCRIPTION: Uses the 'const' processor to resolve the value of a PHP constant named in HEALTH_CHECK_METHOD and use it as the allowed HTTP method for a security access control rule in Symfony's PHP config format. Dependencies are ContainerBuilder and SecurityConfig. Input is a parameter, and output configures security rules.
