TITLE: Configuring Doctrine Event Listeners in XML
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to register a Doctrine event listener using XML configuration in services.xml. It shows the syntax for tagging a service with doctrine.event_listener and setting event, priority, and connection options.
