TITLE: Configuring Services with an Explicit Configurator Method in YAML
DESCRIPTION: This YAML snippet demonstrates how to configure services in `config/services.yaml`. It assumes services are autoconfigured via the `App\:` resource definition. It then explicitly overrides the definitions for `NewsletterManager` and `GreetingCardManager` to use `EmailConfigurator`'s `configure` method as their configurator, specified as an array `['@App\Mail\EmailConfigurator', 'configure']`.
