TITLE: Custom Date Version Strategy Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Example of implementing a custom version strategy that uses the current date for cache busting
SOURCE: https://github.com/symfony/symfony-docs/blob/7.3/components/asset.rst#2025-04-22_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use Symfony\Component\Asset\VersionStrategy\VersionStrategyInterface;

class DateVersionStrategy implements VersionStrategyInterface
{
    private string $version;

    public function __construct()
    {
        $this->version = date('Ymd');
    }

    public function getVersion(string $path): string
    {
        return $this->version;
    }

    public function applyVersion(string $path): string
    {
        return sprintf('%s?v=%s', $path, $this->getVersion($path));
    }
}
```

