TITLE: Implementing Luhn Validation with PHP Method in Symfony
DESCRIPTION: Example of applying the Luhn validation constraint to a credit card number property using PHP method for metadata loading. This approach validates that card numbers comply with the Luhn algorithm.
SOURCE: https://github.com/symfony/symfony-docs/blob/7.3/reference/constraints/Luhn.rst#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
// src/Entity/Transaction.php
namespace App\Entity;

use Symfony\Component\Validator\Constraints as Assert;
use Symfony\Component\Validator\Mapping\ClassMetadata;

class Transaction
{
    // ...

    public static function loadValidatorMetadata(ClassMetadata $metadata): void
    {
