TITLE: Template Rendering Function Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Function that handles template rendering by extracting request attributes and including the appropriate template file based on the route.
SOURCE: https://github.com/symfony/symfony-docs/blob/7.3/create_framework/templating.rst#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
function render_template(Request $request): Response
{
    extract($request->attributes->all(), EXTR_SKIP);
    ob_start();
    include sprintf(__DIR__.'/../src/pages/%s.php', $_route);

    return new Response(ob_get_clean());
}
```

