TITLE: Configuring LessThanOrEqual Constraint in PHP
DESCRIPTION: PHP code for setting up the LessThanOrEqual constraint on 'siblings' and 'age' properties using the loadValidatorMetadata method.
SOURCE: https://github.com/symfony/symfony-docs/blob/7.3/reference/constraints/LessThanOrEqual.rst#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
// src/Entity/Person.php
namespace App\Entity;

use Symfony\Component\Validator\Constraints as Assert;
use Symfony\Component\Validator\Mapping\ClassMetadata;

class Person
{
    // ...

    public static function loadValidatorMetadata(ClassMetadata $metadata): void
    {
        $metadata->addPropertyConstraint('siblings', new Assert\LessThanOrEqual(5));

        $metadata->addPropertyConstraint('age', new Assert\LessThanOrEqual(
            value: 80,
        ));
    }
}
```

