SOURCE: https://github.com/symfony/symfony-docs/blob/7.3/reference/configuration/framework.rst#2025-04-22_snippet_36

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
# config/packages/exceptions.yaml\nframework:\n    exceptions:\n        Exception:\n            log_level: 'debug'\n            status_code: 404\n        # The following configuration will never be used because \RuntimeException extends \Exception\n        RuntimeException:\n            log_level: 'debug'\n            status_code: 422
```

