SOURCE: https://github.com/symfony/symfony-docs/blob/7.3/setup/unstable_versions.rst#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: terminal
CODE:
```
$ cd projects/my_project/\n$ git checkout -b testing_new_symfony\n# ... update composer.json configuration\n$ composer update \"symfony/*\"\n\n# ... after testing the new Symfony version\n$ git checkout master\n$ git branch -D testing_new_symfony
```

