TITLE: Creating a Full Twig Template for Symfony Web Profiler
DESCRIPTION: This Twig template provides a complete implementation for a custom data collector in the Symfony web profiler. It includes blocks for the toolbar, menu, and detailed panel view.
SOURCE: https://github.com/symfony/symfony-docs/blob/7.3/profiler.rst#2025-04-22_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: Twig
CODE:
```
{# templates/data_collector/template.html.twig #}
{% extends '@WebProfiler/Profiler/layout.html.twig' %}

{% block toolbar %}
    {% set icon %}
        {# ... #}
    {% endset %}

    {% set text %}
        <div class="sf-toolbar-info-piece">
            {# ... #}
        </div>
    {% endset %}

    {{ include('@WebProfiler/Profiler/toolbar_item.html.twig', { 'link': true }) }}
{% endblock %}

{% block head %}
    {# Optional. Here you can link to or define your own CSS and JS contents. #}
