TITLE: Enforcing Minimum and Maximum Constraints on Integer and Float Nodes in Symfony TreeBuilder (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: Adds validation constraints (min and max) to integer and float configuration nodes within the Symfony TreeBuilder. This restricts values for numeric fields, ensuring they fall within specified ranges. Requires Symfony Config definitions; inputs are numeric configuration values, which are rejected if outside set bounds. Used in settings where certain configuration fields must stay under or above specified limits.
