LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
$section1 = $output->section();
$section2 = $output->section();

$progress1 = new ProgressBar($section1);
$progress2 = new ProgressBar($section2);

$progress1->start(100);
$progress2->start(100);

$i = 0;
while (++$i < 100) {
    $progress1->advance();

    if ($i % 2 === 0) {
        $progress2->advance(4);
    }

    usleep(50000);
}
```

