TITLE: Configuring Service Decoration in PHP
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to configure service decoration using PHP configuration. The Bar service decorates Foo and uses ContainerInterface::IGNORE_ON_INVALID_REFERENCE to handle missing services.
