TITLE: Integrating IssueToNumberTransformer in TaskType Form in PHP
DESCRIPTION: Updates the TaskType form class to use the custom IssueToNumberTransformer for the 'issue' field. It adds the transformer to the field and sets an invalid_message for validation errors.
